node.text: I made a video to celebrate the new year of amazing things happening on Earth - An Astronaut's Guide to Optimism 2020. I hope you like it!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Hadfield on September 19, 2021. May be an image of 4 people.

node.text: Congrats to these 4 very fortunate people - I look forward to how you will now share the experience to inspire and enable others.  #inspiration4

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Hadfield on September 18, 2021.
Photo by Chris Hadfield on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Congratulations to the world's 4 newest astronauts! Well-done to safely get them there, @SpaceX!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chris Hadfield in Kennedy Space Center Launch Complex 39. May be an image of 1 person, standing and road.

node.text:
Chris, Jared, Hayley and Sian are leaving Earth in 8 hours. None of them are professional astronauts, yet they’ll orbit alone, for 3 days! An amazing new step in spaceflight capability. 
#insparation4 @SpaceX
